The ``$gridshift`` block sets up the routine for the grid-shifting procedure.
unique
none
type
optional
string
The type of grid-shifting procedure (default value is ``default`` - see :doc:`/overview/grid_shifting`).

maxshifts
required
numerical
The maximum number of grid-shifting iterations.
Setting it to zero disables grid-shifting.
mergeable

margins
required
list numerical
The margins :math:`\delta_i` and :math:`\Delta_i` for each grid dimension :math:`i`. The values should be listed in the order :math:`\delta_1`, :math:`\Delta_1`, :math:`\delta_2`, :math:`\Delta_2`, :math:`\cdots`, :math:`\delta_D`, :math:`\Delta_D`.
For type = default.
mergeable

ncut
required
numerical
The value of :math:`n_\text{cut}`.
For type = default.
mergeable
